WEBVTT

00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:20.280
Mr. Hui,

00:01:20.960 --> 00:01:21.890
long time no see.

00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:24.160
Captain Sun.

00:01:25.520 --> 00:01:26.760
You invited us to dinner,

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:27.820
yet you're so late.

00:01:28.600 --> 00:01:30.130
I was too busy with the team.

00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:32.000
And who is this friend?

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:32.360
Oh,

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:33.200
let me introduce you.

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:34.039
This is my colleague,

00:01:34.039 --> 00:01:34.520
Lao Yan.

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:36.300
Have a seat.

00:01:37.080 --> 00:01:37.400
Sit.

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:38.580
Please sit.

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:46.650
Officer Yan,

00:01:46.960 --> 00:01:48.160
please look after us.

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:01.720
Okay.

00:02:02.160 --> 00:02:03.160
What a character.

00:02:07.240 --> 00:02:08.100
I'll keep this.

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:09.220
I'll keep this.

00:02:09.960 --> 00:02:10.919
Our Officer Yan

00:02:10.919 --> 00:02:12.180
is just slow to warm up.

00:02:18.480 --> 00:02:21.410
Since Captain Sun invited us to a hot pot restaurant,

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:22.520
Then that means

00:02:23.079 --> 00:02:24.740
there's no serious business.

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:25.840
Just old friends catching up.

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:26.640
Actually,

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:27.960
there is some serious business.

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:29.640
It's about things from before 2005.

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:30.280
You all

00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:31.640
are entertainment industry

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:32.240
big shots.

00:02:32.440 --> 00:02:34.120
You have wide networks and know many people.

00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:36.450
So I'd like to ask for your help to identify

00:02:38.079 --> 00:02:38.520
this

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:41.120
person in the photo,

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:42.120
and the location.

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:52.520
Hey.

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:54.380
Isn't this that kid Abiao?

00:02:56.720 --> 00:02:57.560
Don't forget,

00:02:58.120 --> 00:02:59.560
we didn't get to where we are today

00:02:59.560 --> 00:03:01.090
by selling out our friends.

00:03:03.160 --> 00:03:04.320
Mr. Hui should know

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.240
that you can't just

00:03:06.240 --> 00:03:07.700
make friends with anyone.

00:03:15.880 --> 00:03:16.610
Officer Yan.

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.360
Is it your business

00:03:19.560 --> 00:03:20.960
who we make friends with?

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:22.560
Dahei, right?

00:03:23.160 --> 00:03:24.020
Do you know him?

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:25.240
Lao Yan.

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:35.560
You know Zhang Biao.

00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:36.820
You used to be friends.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:38.040
Yes.

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:39.560
But so what?

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:41.400
Officer Yan,

00:03:41.880 --> 00:03:43.740
we are law-abiding businessmen,

00:03:43.760 --> 00:03:46.160
not prisoners in your interrogation room.

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:47.620
How about this.

00:03:48.760 --> 00:03:49.760
Bottoms up,

00:03:50.160 --> 00:03:51.360
and let's be friends.

00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:53.640
Maybe

00:03:54.600 --> 00:03:55.930
we can even help you out.

00:03:59.040 --> 00:03:59.400
Hey.

00:03:59.560 --> 00:04:00.320
Mr. Hui, Mr. Hui,

00:04:00.320 --> 00:04:00.960
sorry.

00:04:01.160 --> 00:04:02.240
It's not that we won't drink,

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:03.240
it's just that...

00:04:08.640 --> 00:04:09.000
Hey,

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:10.460
what are you doing?

00:04:11.320 --> 00:04:12.250
What do you mean?

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:18.250
Our police force has rules,

00:04:18.279 --> 00:04:19.040
no drinking.

00:04:19.480 --> 00:04:20.480
I toast this drink

00:04:20.880 --> 00:04:23.320
to those still lying in the morgue,

00:04:23.320 --> 00:04:24.560
including Zhang Biao.

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:26.040
If he knows it in the netherworld.

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:27.300
I know if everyone here

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:28.320
can provide him with clues

00:04:28.320 --> 00:04:29.480
to find the real culprit,

00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:31.140
he will definitely thank you.

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:32.880
I will thank you too.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:40.970
Captain Sun,

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:43.850
what does your friend mean?

00:04:50.520 --> 00:04:51.120
Everyone,

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:52.720
here's the thing.

00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:55.280
The person in this photo

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:57.060
is related to a major case.

00:04:57.320 --> 00:04:58.520
It involves several lives

00:04:58.520 --> 00:05:00.650
and even the safety of our entire city.

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:02.800
I really hope you can do me a favor

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:04.360
and help provide some clues.

00:05:04.360 --> 00:05:05.280
Recognize the person

00:05:05.280 --> 00:05:06.010
or the place.

00:05:06.320 --> 00:05:08.400
We do have strict rules against drinking.

00:05:08.400 --> 00:05:09.040
Tell you what.

00:05:09.040 --> 00:05:10.120
I'll drink tea instead of alcohol.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:11.450
I'll finish this glass.

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:33.240
Thanks for doing us the honor, Captain Sun.

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:33.760
Dahei.

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:35.370
You said you recognize him.

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:36.200
Tell us about him.

00:05:36.200 --> 00:05:38.130
Introduce him to the two officers.

00:05:38.280 --> 00:05:41.080
His build and clothes look a bit familiar.

00:05:41.400 --> 00:05:42.840
I remember he was quite a big spender.

00:05:42.840 --> 00:05:43.700
He's a big boss.

00:05:44.159 --> 00:05:46.000
This guy came to my club a few times before,

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.159
but he thought my place was too tame,

00:05:47.159 --> 00:05:48.240
so he stopped coming.

00:05:48.240 --> 00:05:49.170
Tell us his name.

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:50.760
Let our two friends know.

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:51.920
His name...

00:05:51.920 --> 00:05:52.960
I don't remember his name.

00:05:52.960 --> 00:05:54.320
He works in the medical field.

00:05:54.320 --> 00:05:55.580
He seemed like a fraud.

00:05:56.520 --> 00:05:58.120
Do you recognize this place?

00:05:58.600 --> 00:05:59.120
Mr. Hui,

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:00.000
take a look.

00:06:01.480 --> 00:06:02.160
Such a

00:06:02.280 --> 00:06:03.280
hidden space,

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:06.680
people in the same business wouldn't normally talk about it.

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:07.880
What about that girl?

00:06:07.880 --> 00:06:09.480
The girl who was pinned down.

00:06:11.080 --> 00:06:12.680
The girl on the coffee table?

00:06:13.240 --> 00:06:14.000
No face.

00:06:14.520 --> 00:06:15.720
Can't recognize her.

00:06:16.440 --> 00:06:17.760
There are so many girls in the club.

00:06:17.760 --> 00:06:18.720
There are dozens or hundreds of them.

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:19.780
Who would know her?

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:21.520
At least show some cleavage.

00:06:21.560 --> 00:06:22.720
Without showing any,

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:23.850
how would I know her?

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:26.220
Please show some respect.

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:27.370
She's a human being,

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:28.560
just like you.

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:30.040
Everyone has a name.

00:06:30.040 --> 00:06:31.500
People call me Brother Fu.

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:32.400
What about her?

00:06:32.400 --> 00:06:33.520
What's her name?

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:35.400
If you knew who she was,

00:06:35.640 --> 00:06:37.100
you wouldn't be asking us.

00:06:38.680 --> 00:06:39.210
Hey, hey.

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:41.409
Captain Sun.

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:43.610
Your colleague has quite a temper.

00:06:43.960 --> 00:06:45.290
I'm sorry, Brother Hui.

00:06:45.480 --> 00:06:46.200
Um,

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:47.280
We have to go now.

00:06:47.560 --> 00:06:47.920
What do you mean?

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:48.280
I've paid the bill.

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:49.210
Enjoy your meal.

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:09.490
You are still like this.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:12.860
You don't like dealing with such people.

00:07:16.840 --> 00:07:17.600
I don't.

00:07:19.200 --> 00:07:21.000
Humans are the most complicated

00:07:21.400 --> 00:07:22.860
and terrifying creatures

00:07:23.200 --> 00:07:24.200
in the world.

00:07:27.880 --> 00:07:29.120
In our line of work,

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:30.520
for a few clues,

00:07:30.600 --> 00:07:32.120
we have to deal with

00:07:32.159 --> 00:07:33.520
all kinds of people.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:43.600
Master

00:07:45.640 --> 00:07:46.880
used to say that too.

00:08:01.560 --> 00:08:03.620
I used to hate it when he was like this.

00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:06.730
But unconsciously,

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.560
I seem to have become him.

00:08:17.840 --> 00:08:18.640
But at least

00:08:18.640 --> 00:08:20.370
I got some useful information.

00:08:20.640 --> 00:08:21.840
According to what he said,

00:08:21.840 --> 00:08:23.600
the man with the side profile in the photo is a big boss

00:08:23.600 --> 00:08:25.000
in the medical business,

00:08:25.200 --> 00:08:27.240
and his phone number should be a lucky one.

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:28.920
If we screen Hao Weiguo's contacts,

00:08:28.920 --> 00:08:30.250
we can find him quickly.

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:21.760
Liar!

00:09:21.960 --> 00:09:22.920
Stop right there!

00:09:22.920 --> 00:09:24.240
Who are you? Why are you grabbing me?

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:25.440
Your treatment killed my daughter.

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:25.880
What are you doing?

00:09:25.880 --> 00:09:27.360
Pay for my daughter's life!

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:28.440
Wait, who is your daughter?

00:09:28.440 --> 00:09:29.760
Who are you? Why are you holding me?

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:30.520
You killed her with your treatment.

00:09:30.520 --> 00:09:31.160
Let go of me.

00:09:31.160 --> 00:09:32.680
You said the medicine would cure her.

00:09:32.680 --> 00:09:34.200
You even told me to keep giving it to her.

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:35.600
You are a liar.

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:36.560
You are a bastard.

00:09:36.560 --> 00:09:37.000
Let me tell you.

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:39.080
Your daughter's death has nothing to do with me.

00:09:39.080 --> 00:09:40.480
No one can stop God from taking a life.

00:09:40.480 --> 00:09:41.200
If you move again...

00:09:41.200 --> 00:09:43.260
Move again, and I'll take you out too.

00:09:46.280 --> 00:09:47.880
The match's name is Liu Jiang.

00:09:47.880 --> 00:09:48.720
He used to be a doctor.

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:50.680
Made a lot of money selling health products.

00:09:50.680 --> 00:09:52.360
In 2006, for illegal trading,

00:09:52.360 --> 00:09:53.160
he was sentenced to three years in prison.

00:09:53.160 --> 00:09:55.000
All his illegal gains were confiscated.

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:55.960
He was released the year before last.

00:09:55.960 --> 00:09:56.800
But he didn't learn his lesson.

00:09:56.800 --> 00:09:59.080
He still hangs out at the hospital every day, looking for people to scam.

00:09:59.080 --> 00:10:00.040
Also, we found

00:10:00.040 --> 00:10:03.040
that he withdrew a large amount of cash last year using a certificate of deposit.

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:04.560
The time of this cash withdrawal

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:07.220
matches the time Cripple Hao received the cash.

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:09.970
This is a photo of him before he went to prison.

00:10:12.160 --> 00:10:13.280
He used to be a doctor.

00:10:13.280 --> 00:10:14.040
He's smart.

00:10:15.560 --> 00:10:17.760
He just didn't use it in the right place.

00:10:21.800 --> 00:10:22.640
Liu Jiang.

00:10:23.240 --> 00:10:23.760
Let's go.

00:10:23.760 --> 00:10:24.820
Let's go catch him.

00:10:26.040 --> 00:10:27.440
Security.

00:10:27.520 --> 00:10:28.160
Police.

00:10:29.720 --> 00:10:30.240
Do you

00:10:30.320 --> 00:10:31.120
know this man?

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:32.440
Isn't that Liu Jiang?

00:10:32.440 --> 00:10:33.960
Didn't he give you a carton of cigarettes yesterday?

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:34.800
Don't talk nonsense.

00:10:34.800 --> 00:10:36.080
I wouldn't accept cigarettes from others.

00:10:36.080 --> 00:10:37.120
Where does he usually hang out?

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:38.720
Turn right here into the first alley.

00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:39.850
He's usually there.

00:10:50.120 --> 00:10:50.760
Oh.

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:55.480
This is great.

00:10:57.760 --> 00:10:58.400
Handsome.

00:10:59.640 --> 00:11:01.900
Why are you wearing a mask and trembling?

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:03.440
Are you feeling unwell?

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:04.160
Dr. Liu.

00:11:04.240 --> 00:11:05.640
The doctors in this hospital

00:11:05.640 --> 00:11:07.360
say my heart condition is incurable.

00:11:07.360 --> 00:11:08.520
It is curable.

00:11:08.680 --> 00:11:10.480
You're lucky to have met me.

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:12.000
How does the old saying go?

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:13.840
There is great medicine in the world.

00:11:13.840 --> 00:11:15.040
Your fate is in your hands,

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:16.200
not heaven's.

00:11:17.280 --> 00:11:18.520
Who is this great medicine?

00:11:18.520 --> 00:11:20.080
It is me.

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:21.640
I can cure all diseases.

00:11:21.680 --> 00:11:22.200
Trust me.

00:11:22.200 --> 00:11:23.600
Let me prescribe some medicine for you to try, okay?

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:24.120
Okay.

00:11:24.120 --> 00:11:24.840
You try it first.

00:11:24.840 --> 00:11:25.600
The light is a bit dim.

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:27.240
I'll go write it for you over here.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:28.040
Wait a moment.

00:11:28.280 --> 00:11:29.740
I'll write it down for you.

00:11:31.000 --> 00:11:32.000
Well...

00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:33.680
These are all secret recipes.

00:11:33.680 --> 00:11:35.240
I usually only pass them down to sons, not daughters.

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:36.240
It is a bit pricey.

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:36.960
Trust me.

00:11:36.960 --> 00:11:37.760
It'll be fine.

00:11:39.800 --> 00:11:40.240
Captain Sun.

00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:41.560
Come back when it's done.

00:11:41.560 --> 00:11:42.320
I found something.

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:42.720
Done.

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:43.320
That's it.

00:11:43.320 --> 00:11:43.680
Hey, no.

00:11:43.680 --> 00:11:44.040
Hey!

00:11:44.200 --> 00:11:45.800
Hey man, where are you going?

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:46.440
Hey!

00:11:46.440 --> 00:11:47.680
You don't want your prescription?

00:11:47.680 --> 00:11:48.400
Liu Jiang!

00:11:49.840 --> 00:11:50.320
What?

00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:51.600
Liu Jiang!

00:11:58.240 --> 00:11:59.360
Chasing me again.

00:12:23.600 --> 00:12:24.460
I'm exhausted.

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:33.520
Run!

00:12:33.640 --> 00:12:34.480
You big guy!

00:12:34.520 --> 00:12:35.200
You... Damn it.

00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:36.160
I'll smash you!

00:12:38.960 --> 00:12:39.560
Stop!

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:40.800
Liu Jiang!

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:41.480
Stop!

00:12:45.000 --> 00:12:46.130
Why are you running?

00:12:52.760 --> 00:12:53.400
Liu Jiang!

00:12:53.720 --> 00:12:54.400
Liu Jiang!

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:03.560
Guard the door.

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:06.120
Stop chasing me!

00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:21.640
Hurry up.

00:13:21.640 --> 00:13:22.880
Hurry up.

00:13:24.040 --> 00:13:24.640
Liu Jiang!

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:27.320
Liu Jiang!

00:13:33.240 --> 00:13:33.800
Take the stairs.

00:13:33.800 --> 00:13:34.280
Okay.

00:13:47.920 --> 00:13:49.120
Here we go again.

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:50.780
Why are you always chasing me?

00:13:56.160 --> 00:13:57.480
Stop chasing me.

00:13:57.480 --> 00:13:58.120
My legs are going to break.

00:13:58.120 --> 00:13:59.040
Liu Jiang, don't run.

00:13:59.040 --> 00:13:59.640
Stop chasing.

00:13:59.640 --> 00:14:01.280
Why are you chasing me?

00:14:01.600 --> 00:14:02.520
Stop chasing.

00:14:08.920 --> 00:14:09.880
Chase.

00:14:16.280 --> 00:14:17.200
Sorry, kid.

00:14:23.400 --> 00:14:24.280
It's fine.

00:14:24.960 --> 00:14:25.600
It's fine.

00:14:25.800 --> 00:14:26.440
Captain Sun.

00:14:26.440 --> 00:14:27.880
Liu Jiang went to the underground parking lot.